Updated `website/src/pages/index.module.css` to raise the diagram-panel readability inside the `Transit Network Shape` card.

Contrast changes:
- brighter foreground color for `.sceneDiagram`
- heavier and slightly larger monospace type
- reduced text-shadow heaviness
- simplified, slightly cleaner deep-blue panel background

The lineage box now uses a more explicit high-contrast treatment rather than a subdued dark panel.
